cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper uses natural language processing methodology to analyze emotional trajectories of movies and predict their success parameters. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques to cluster emotional journeys and predict success parameters, which falls under the categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses implications for business model innovation in entertainment industries, which could fall under the categories of cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
